description: Removes key-value tag pairs associated to your Amazon Managed Workflows for Apache Airflow (MWAA) environment. For example, "Environment": "Staging".

parameters.name: ResourceArn
parameters.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the Amazon MWAA environment. For example, arn:aws:airflow:us-east-1:123456789012:environment/MyMWAAEnvironment.

parameters.name: tagKeys
parameters.description: The key-value tag pair you want to remove. For example, "Environment": "Staging". (string) ---
